caller_intent: Josefina Luna requested assistance with car insurance information and needed to speak with someone who speaks Spanish.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the caller's request to speak with someone in Spanish.
Agent informed caller there were no current Spanish-speaking agents available.
Agent offered to have someone call back and requested the caller's phone number.
Agent confirmed receipt of the number and assured follow-up.
summary: Josefina Luna called to request car insurance information and Spanish-language support. The agent could not immediately assist but arranged for a callback. The caller provided her contact information, and the agent confirmed follow-up.
